  <acronym>MACS2002</acronym>
  <official_title>Extension Study to the &quot;Open-label Phase I Study Evaluating the Safety and Tolerability of Pasireotide LAR in Combination With Everolimus in Advanced Metastatic NETs - The COOPERATE-1 Study&quot;</official_title>
