  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate long-term safety and tolerability of pasireotide LAR in combination
      with everolimus in advanced metastatic NET patients, who who have not progressed during 12
      months of combination therapy with pasireotide LAR and everolimus
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
